snippet.title: I Tried Bill Gates Think Week!
snippet.description:
I Tried Bill Gates Think Week!
The first 100 people to go to https://blinkist.com/kallehallden are going to get unlimited access for 1 week to try it out. You’ll also get 25% off if you want the full membership.

I went to Norway and did a Bill Gates Think Week.

"Clean Code Friday"
If you want to receive one short email from me every week, where I go through a few of the most useful things I have explored and discovered this week. Things like; favourite apps, articles, podcasts, books, coding tips and tricks. Then feel free to join https://kalletech.com/cleancode/

CONTACT: halldenkalle@gmail.com
